headline: Health Net and Centene Corporation (CNC) Commit Over $7.2 Million to Boost Healthcare Access Through Mobile Clinics in California
summary: Health Net and the Centene Corporation (NYSE:CNC)’s philanthropic arm, Centene Foundation, have announced a major $7.2 million investment to expand healthcare access for underserved Californians through a new fleet of mobile health clinics.
